metadata.name: Coffee please?
metadata.description:
Who doesn't love some single origin coffee? Brazil? Ethiopia? Kenya? PNG? 

Nothing beats this native Thai, Cara who loves sipping on coffee during our photoshoot. She enjoys cool beverages in hot weathers, just like our session in sunny Singapore. 

Cara visited for a few days and we decided to make full use of her visit, and to create art that we both envision.
